<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1952-12-31T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-11-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="881" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d881">
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                            </head>
                            <p>The United States Congress authorized the transfer of two destroyer
                                escorts to Uruguay under Public Law 146, approved September 15,
                                1951; for text, see 65 Stat. 322. The sale of the ships was effected
                                on November 15. Pertinent documents are in Department of State
                                decimal file 733.5-<gloss target="#t_MAP1">MAP</gloss>.</p>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>